<i>adverb</i>: 자상히 [자상히], 유심히 [유ː심히], 세심히 [세ː심히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>자상히 [자상히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. minutely; in detail</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하고 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a meticulous and detailed manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. considerately; attentively; thoughtfully</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 많고 온갖 힘을 다하려는 마음이 깊게.</dd><br>
<dd>With compassion for others and a sincere mind to do all one can for them.</dd><br>
<dt>유심히 [유ː심히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mindfully</dd><br>
<dd>마음속에 품고 있는 뜻이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>With something in one's mind.</dd><br>
<dd>2. carefully; attentively</dd><br>
<dd>주의가 깊게.</dd><br>
<dd>With care and attention.</dd><br>
<dt>세심히 [세ː심히]</dt><br>
<dd>attentively; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>작은 일에도 매우 꼼꼼하게 주의를 기울여 빈틈이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a attentive and careful manner of doing a small thing, leaving nothing untouched.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>